              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Set NOCOUNT ON",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": This command prevents the SQL Server from sending messages about the number of rows affected by the "
